---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="Voxeia Privacy Policy - How we collect, use, and protect your data.">
  <section class="relative pt-32 pb-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary uppercase tracking-wider">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black text-text">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-text-muted">Last updated: February 21, 2026</p>

      <div class="mt-12 prose max-w-none space-y-8">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            We collect information you provide directly to us, including your name, email address, phone number, company
            name, and payment information when you create an account, subscribe to a plan, or contact us.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mt-3">
            We also automatically collect certain information when you use our services, including call metadata, usage
            patterns, device information, IP addresses, and browser type.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-text-muted">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary mt-1">•</span> To provide, maintain, and improve our AI calling services
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary mt-1">•</span> To process transactions and send billing information
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary mt-1">•</span> To send technical notices, updates, and support messages
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary mt-1">•</span> To train and improve our AI models (anonymized data only)
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary mt-1">•</span> To comply with legal obligations and enforce our terms
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-4">3. Data Sharing</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            We do not sell your personal information. We may share data with third-party service providers who assist in
            operating our platform (e.g., payment processors, cloud hosting, analytics). All third parties are bound by
            strict data processing agreements.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-4">4. Data Security</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            We implement industry-standard security measures including AES-256 encryption at rest, TLS 1.3 in transit,
            regular security audits, and SOC 2 Type II compliance. Call recordings are encrypted and stored in ISO 27001
            certified data centers.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-4">5. Data Retention</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            We retain your account information for as long as your account is active. Call recordings and transcripts
            are retained for 90 days by default, configurable up to 365 days. You can request deletion of your data at
            any time.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-4">6. Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            Depending on your location, you may have rights to access, correct, delete, or port your personal data. You
            can also opt out of marketing communications at any time. To exercise these rights, contact us at
            privacy@voxeia.com.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-4">7. Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            For any privacy-related questions or concerns, please contact our Data Protection Officer at
            privacy@voxeia.com or write to us at Sector 62, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201301, India.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
